    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but honestly it feels like overkill since the infection is literally gone. like, if the bacteria are dead, then the medicine isn't doing anything anymore, right? my friend said that if you feel 100% better, you can just switch to vitamins or something to help your immune system instead. if i stop now, am i actually at risk or is that just being super cautious?",
